# NOTE (rework/full-source-sync):
# The website source (index.html, playbook.html, *.jsx, content.jsx, fonts,
# favicon) used to be gitignored as "deployed to VPS, not in repo." That made
# the repo non-self-contained: CI cannot run scripts/build-lessons.js (needs
# content.jsx) and cannot deploy the homepage/reader. To enable CI deploy and
# keep one source of truth, those files are now tracked. The lesson content is
# already public via playbook.md / playbook.json / llms-full.txt, so this
# exposes no new content. If you'd rather keep website source out of the public
# repo, re-add the entries below and deploy that source to the VPS out-of-band:
#   website/index.html  website/playbook.html  website/*.jsx
#   website/fonts/  website/favicon.svg
